ActJudges Act (Removal Allowance) Order
PrecisOrder prescribing an additional period during which certain RELOCATION EXPENSES may be reimbursed to The Hon. JEAN-PAUL OUELLETTE, who was required to relocate to the city of Miramichi in New Brunswick following his appointment as a Judge of the Court of Queen's Bench of New Brunswick, Family Division, on April 11, 2008.
